{
  "name": "RPlog_Changing_The_Guard",
  "title": "Changing the Guard at the Meltdown",
  "summary": "A quiet evening of tense drinks at the Meltdown Cafe on Nar Shaddaa erupts into a full-scale brawl when a Sith-backed coup against Grubba the Hutt spills through the doors. The Sith Tyler Damion, fighting under the alias 'Tatooine Bob,' is hurled into the bar by Grubba's towering Wookiee bodyguard, and the patrons, the soldier Sarray, the reporter Eithne, the exiled gunman Dareus, the smug Twi'lek Via, the crime lord Thanos, the drunken pirate Juran, the surgeon-commodore Lynae, the grumbling medic Xar'on, arms dealer Kaitlin, the silent Tritus, and the bloodthirsty pilot Axel Vichten, are forced to fight for their lives. The Wookiee and Grubba's thugs are slaughtered, Lynae mercy-kills the dying as Xar'on storms off in disgust, and Thanos declares the cafe the seed of his new regime. With the system locked down by Axel's fleet, the survivors regroup over looted drinks, reckoning their tangled loyalties to the Sith, the Maffi, and each other before scattering into the war-torn streets.",
